race.description: Soul Food Depot & Gallery Maiden Plate
race.comment: SWEDISH GLITTER (9) eight-start maiden working her way into form. Not that far away again when fifth over 900m at Wellington. Leading chance with the claim from the good gate. DER BLAUE REITER (12) resumes from a spell of six months. Back without a trial after finishing a close up fourth over 900m at Newcastle on the heavy (8) surface. Has the ratings to win first up. ALLY ALLEY ALI (10) two-year-old filly by King's Legacy out of Dream Genie on debut for the Connie Greig yard. Fitted with the two trials, including a win over 900m at Wellington. Finds a winnable contest from the inside gate. SNOWBALL (8) had genuine excuses from the outside gate at latest when seventh over 900m at Wellington. Gets the claim again from the low draw. Each way.
